 .../TTNN/Transforms/TTNNCheckDRAMBudget.cpp   | 129 ++++++++++++++++++
 .../Dialect/TTNN/Pipelines/TTNNPipelines.cpp  |   4 +
 .../Dialect/TTNN/Transforms/CMakeLists.txt    |   1 +
